name: Let's Developer
body: Software Engineering is not programming. It's a difficult and challenging discipline, which you only learn through practice. Lots of practice. You can gain experience on your own, but only so much. You'll learn more and faster, if you talk to and work with others. And that's what Let's Develop is about. Join me! Let's Developer on Google+
